                <Header>Funds</Header>
                <Paragraph>TSP participants may opt to invest their retirement dollars in one or more of five individual funds: the Common Stock Index Investment Fund (C), Fixed Income Index Investment Fund (F), Government Securities Investment Fund (G), International Stock Index Investment Fund (I), and Small Cap Stock Index Investment Fund (S).</Paragraph>
